      "writtenOn": "2020-02-28T19:33:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not a fan of putting Fatal calls this far down stack. I expect if this were to happen, there would be much much bigger deals (like Firestore completely down). For expectationstore, we have a metric that is a counter that is incremented if this happens. I think (?) we have an alert if that metric becomes non-zero. I could add such a thing if you desire (in a followup CL).",
